    <section>
      <h2>Why Jobsolv Wins</h2>

      <h3>1. Per-Job Resume Tailoring</h3>
      <p>LinkedIn uses your profile or a single uploaded resume for all applications. Jobsolv customizes your resume for every job, matching keywords and skills from each job description. This significantly improves ATS pass rates and interview conversion.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Generic applications get lost in LinkedIn's competitive pool → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Higher interview rates with targeted applications</p>

      <h3>2. Less Competition</h3>
      <p>LinkedIn has millions of active job seekers competing for the same roles. Jobsolv's specialized remote/hybrid focus means less competition per job. You're not competing against the entire LinkedIn user base.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Getting lost among hundreds of applicants → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Better visibility in less crowded marketplace</p>

      <h3>3. Integrated Application Tools</h3>
      <p>Job board, resume builder, tailoring, and tracking in one place. LinkedIn requires you to manage profile, networking, job browsing, and applications separately. Jobsolv streamlines the entire application process.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Managing multiple disconnected tools and processes → <strong>Outcome:</strong> One platform for browsing, tailoring, and applying</p>

      <h3>4. Free Access to Core Features</h3>
      <p>LinkedIn's free tier has limitations, and premium features cost extra. Jobsolv's free tier includes the job board, resume builder, job tracker, and limited resume tailoring. You can start applying immediately without payment.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Premium features required for effective job search → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Start applying with full features at zero cost</p>

      <h3>5. Specialized Remote/Hybrid Focus</h3>
      <p>Jobsolv curates remote and hybrid roles paying $100K+, updated daily. LinkedIn has all job types, requiring extensive filtering. Jobsolv saves time by focusing on roles that match your preferences.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Wasting time filtering through irrelevant jobs → <strong>Outcome:</strong> See only relevant remote/hybrid high-paying roles</p>
    </section>

