      <h3>Company Research and Insights</h3>
      <p>LinkedIn provides comprehensive company pages, employee insights, salary data, and company culture information. Jobsolv offers basic company overviews. For deep company research, LinkedIn is superior.</p>

      <h3>Job Market Size</h3>
      <p>LinkedIn has the largest job marketplace with millions of listings across all industries and locations. Jobsolv focuses on remote/hybrid roles, so the job pool is smaller but more targeted.</p>
